---
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/reskin/PageHero.astro";
import ClientTestimonials from "../components/reskin/ClientTestimonials.astro";
import AwardsBand from "../components/reskin/AwardsBand.astro";
import WCtaBand from "../components/reskin/WCtaBand.astro";
import Picture from "../components/Picture.astro";
import { existsSync } from "node:fs";
import path from "node:path";

const team = (await getCollection("team"))
  .filter((m) => existsSync(path.join(process.cwd(), "public", m.data.portrait)))
  .sort((a, b) => (a.data.order ?? 100) - (b.data.order ?? 100));

const gallery = [
  { src: "/images/office/office-collab-01.jpg", alt: "Two Rooftop team members reviewing work on screen", span: true },
  { src: "/images/office/office-work-01.jpg", alt: "A social campaign for TC Matthews in progress" },
  { src: "/images/office/office-portrait-01.jpg", alt: "A Rooftop team member at work in the studio" },
  { src: "/images/office/office-collab-02.jpg", alt: "Two Rooftop team members collaborating on a laptop" },
  { src: "/images/office/office-work-02.jpg", alt: "Irish Landmark Trust content alongside campaign analytics" },
];

const values = [
  { title: "Owners, not vendors", body: "We work like we're part of your team, invested in your growth." },
  { title: "Everything in-house", body: "Strategy, brand, web, paid, and content under one roof. One joined-up team, no hand-offs." },
  { title: "Accountable to outcomes", body: "We measure success the way you do: pipeline, revenue, and results that compound over time." },
];
---

<Layout title="About Us | Rooftop Twenty Two, Dublin" description="Meet Rooftop Twenty Two, an independent branding, web, and performance marketing studio in Dublin. A senior, in-house team that treats your growth as our own.">
  <PageHero
    kicker="About us"
    title="We&rsquo;re your <em>outsourced growth team</em>."
    intro="Rooftop Twenty Two is an independent studio that develops brands, strategies, and experiences for exceptional companies, plugging into your business like an in-house team."
    bg="/images/office/office-studio-01.jpg"
  />

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="ab-story" id="story">
    <div class="ab-story__inner">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="kicker kicker--script">Our story</p>
        <h2 class="ab-h2">From a bedroom in 2020 to a <em>team of 17</em>.</h2>
        <figure class="ab-story__sign">
          <img src="/images/hero/Cathal.png" alt="Cathal O&rsquo;Reilly, founder of Rooftop Twenty Two" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <figcaption>Cathal O&rsquo;Reilly<span>Founder</span></figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-story__body reveal">
        <p>
          Before Rooftop Twenty Two, I spent more than ten years working in
          marketing agencies. I was hooked on business the whole way through.
          Podcasts, marketing books, new tools, the systems that help a business
          grow. What stuck with me was how overwhelming marketing felt for most
          owners and marketing managers. Endless channels, endless opinions,
          endless distractions.
        </p>
        <p>
          The businesses that did well weren&rsquo;t always the ones spending the
          most. They were the ones with a clear plan. Knowing where the demand is.
          Knowing what customers are searching for. Putting the right message in
          front of the right people at the right time. That simplicity is what
          Rooftop Twenty Two is built on.
        </p>
        <p>
          In July 2019, just after getting married, I told my wife I&rsquo;d start
          my own business within six months. Then I made the mistake of telling
          everyone else. Friends, family, colleagues. Everyone knew. After that,
          there was no turning back. So in January 2020, Rooftop Twenty Two was
          born.
        </p>
        <p>
          Three months later, the world changed. COVID pushed everything online
          almost overnight, and businesses needed websites, digital marketing,
          e-commerce, and visibility more than ever. We were lucky to be in a
          position to help.
        </p>
        <p>
          What started as one person in a bedroom grew through referrals,
          recommendations, and good work delivered month after month. Today
          we&rsquo;re a team of 17 working from our studio in Glasnevin, supporting
          businesses across Ireland and beyond.
        </p>
        <p>
          We&rsquo;ve never leaned on hard sell or big promises. The growth has come
          from doing right by clients, being honest when the conversation is
          difficult, and being able to stand over our work every single month.
          Many of the clients who backed us in the early days are still with us.
          That loyalty means everything, and we never take it for granted.
        </p>
        <p>
          Marketing keeps changing. AI, automation, data, shifting customer
          behaviour. For businesses willing to adapt, that is a real opportunity.
          Our job is to help you cut through the noise, focus on what matters, and
          build marketing that delivers real results.
        </p>
        <p>
          We&rsquo;re proud of what we&rsquo;ve built so far. We&rsquo;re even more
          excited about what&rsquo;s next. If you want a partner who genuinely cares
          about your business and is set on helping you grow, we&rsquo;d love to hear
          from you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <AwardsBand />

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="ab-vals" id="how-we-work">
    <div class="ab-vals__inner">
      <p class="kicker kicker--on-dark kicker--script">What we&rsquo;re about</p>
      <h2 class="ab-h2 ab-vals__title">Performance, people, purpose.</h2>
      <div class="ab-vals__grid">
        {values.map((v, i) => (
          <div class="ab-val reveal">
            <span class="ab-val__n">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, "0")}</span>
            <h3 class="ab-val__title">{v.title}</h3>
            <p class="ab-val__body">{v.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Life at the studio -->
  <section class="ab-life">
    <div class="ab-life__inner">
      <p class="kicker kicker--script">Life at the studio</p>
      <h2 class="ab-h2 ab-mb">Heads down, ideas up.</h2>
      <div class="ab-life__grid">
        {gallery.map((g) => (
          <figure class:list={["ab-shot", g.span ? "ab-shot--wide" : ""]}>
            <Picture src={g.src} alt={g.alt} loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="ab-team" id="team">
    <div class="ab-team__inner">
      <p class="kicker kicker--script">Meet the team</p>
      <h2 class="ab-h2 ab-mb">The people behind the work.</h2>
      <ul class="ab-team__grid">
        {team.map((m) => (
          <li class="reveal">
            <figure class:list={["ab-member", m.data.name === "Justin" && "ab-member--static"]}>
              <div class="ab-member__img"><Picture src={m.data.portrait} alt={m.data.name} loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
              <figcaption>
                <p class="ab-member__name">{m.data.name}</p>
                <p class="ab-member__role">{m.data.role}</p>
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ClientTestimonials />
  <WCtaBand />
</Layout>

<style>
  .ab-h2 { font-family: var(--w-font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: var(--lh-heading); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display); margin: 0.5rem 0 0; }
  .ab-h2 em { font-style: italic; }
  .ab-mb { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

  .ab-story { background: var(--c-bg); color: var(--c-ink); padding-block: var(--w-section-y); }
  .ab-story__inner { max-width: var(--w-container); margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: var(--w-gutter); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  @media (min-width: 900px) { .ab-story__inner { grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr; gap: 4rem; } }
  .ab-story__body p { font-family: var(--w-font-body); font-size: var(--fs-body); line-height: 1.75; color: var(--c-ink-soft); margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .ab-story__sign { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.85rem; margin: 1.75rem 0 0; }
  .ab-story__sign img { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 18%; background: var(--c-bg-alt); }
  .ab-story__sign figcaption { font-family: var(--w-font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--c-ink); line-height: 1.25; }
  .ab-story__sign figcaption span { display: block; font-family: var(--w-font-body); font-weight: 400; font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--c-ink-soft); }

  .ab-vals { background: var(--c-dark); color: var(--c-on-dark); padding-block: var(--w-section-y); }
  .ab-vals__inner { max-width: var(--w-container); margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: var(--w-gutter); }
  .ab-vals__title { color: var(--c-on-dark); }
  .ab-vals__grid { margin-top: 3rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .ab-vals__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 3rem; } }
  .ab-val__n { font-family: var(--w-font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--c-accent-2); }
  .ab-val__title { font-family: var(--w-font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--fs-h3); color: var(--c-on-dark); margin: 0.75rem 0 0; }
  .ab-val__body { font-family: var(--w-font-body); font-size: var(--fs-body); color: var(--c-on-dark-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0.75rem 0 0; }

  .ab-life { background: var(--c-bg-alt); color: var(--c-ink); padding-block: var(--w-section-y); }
  .ab-life__inner { max-width: var(--w-container); margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: var(--w-gutter); }
  .ab-life__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .ab-life__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); grid-auto-rows: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; } }
  .ab-shot { margin: 0; border: 1px solid var(--c-line); border-radius: var(--w-radius); overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 1; }
  .ab-shot--wide { grid-column: span 2; }
  /* On desktop the lead shot becomes a 2×2 anchor so the five images tile two
   * clean rows of four with no empty cells. */
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .ab-shot--wide { grid-row: span 2; aspect-ratio: auto; } }
  .ab-shot img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }

  .ab-team { background: var(--c-bg); color: var(--c-ink); padding-block: var(--w-section-y); }
  .ab-team__inner { max-width: var(--w-container); margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: var(--w-gutter); }
  .ab-team__grid { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
  @media (min-width: 640px) { .ab-team__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1000px) { .ab-team__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; } }
  .ab-member { margin: 0; }
  .ab-member__img { border-radius: var(--w-radius); overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 5 / 6; background: var(--c-bg-alt); }
  .ab-member__img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 18%; filter: grayscale(1); transition: filter var(--w-dur) var(--w-ease), transform var(--w-dur) var(--w-ease); }
  .ab-member:hover .ab-member__img img { filter: grayscale(0); transform: scale(1.03); }
  .ab-member--static:hover .ab-member__img img { filter: grayscale(1); transform: none; }
  .ab-member__name { font-family: var(--w-font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--c-ink); margin: 0.85rem 0 0; }
  .ab-member__role { font-family: var(--w-font-body); font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--c-ink-soft); margin: 0.2rem 0 0; }
</style>
